    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_2209929350358833024.png",
                "id": "talent54150",
                "key": "Favonius Bladework - Maid",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Favonius Bladework - Maid"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span> dan menciptakan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Full Plate</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Full Plate</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p>Memberikan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2 poin</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Perisai</span> untuk Karakter aktifmu. <br>Sebelum <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Perisai</span> ini terkonsumsi sepenuhnya, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> yang kamu terima adalah setengahnya. <br>(Dibulatkan ke atas)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/b6fb31387815c4484390c7fb11891609_3971161161435469333.png",
                "id": "talent9009",
                "key": "Breastplate",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Breastplate"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 4 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>. Karakter ini menerima <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sweeping Time</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Sweeping Time</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>Saat Karaktermu menggunakan Normal Attack: Mengonsumsi 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Dadu Geo</span> lebih sedikit. (Sekali setiap Ronde)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Normal Attack</span> Karakter Karakter mengakibatkan +2 poin DMG, dan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> yang diakibatkannya diubah menjadi <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/cb9d679d3462bed59d1601663836a019_8153672603088745904.png",
                "id": "talent6508",
                "key": "Sweeping Time",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sweeping Time"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_7729950389509139148.png",
                "id": "talent7040",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Perisai</span></strong></p><p>Saat Karakter yang dilindungi Perisai menerima DMG, Perisai akan terkonsumsi untuk menahan DMG yang diterima.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span></strong></p><p>Setiap kali kamu mencapai Tahap Selesai di setiap Ronde, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> -1.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> habis.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8446353516431093650.png",
                "id": "talent39478",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
